All files within each individual participant folder are .csv format. 

Folders:
Data we used in the manuscript. The columns are:
	* pertSize: which refers to the stimulus magnitude of each perceptual task. Unit: mm
	* reactionTime: refers to the time from the task star cue to participants' choice. Unit: s
	* initialResponse: this variable is -1 when the participant chose "left is slower" and 1 when the choice was "right is slower"

Additional there is a file named Dataset.csv, which contains a table compiling all the participant information analyzed in the manuscript.  

